                    <h3>Project 2: Hangman Game</h3>
                    <br>
                    <p>My Python-based Hangman game is an interactive word-guessing game where players try to figure out
                        a hidden word by guessing letters within a limited number of attempts. The program selects a
                        random word from a predefined list, displays the word as a series of blanks, and updates the
                        blanks with correct guesses. Incorrect guesses result in a "hangman" figure being drawn piece by
                        piece. The game continues until the player either guesses the word correctly or uses up all
                        their attempts</p>
                    <br>
